        dc:description           "Figure 4. Paramphimonhystrella minor sp. nov. (A) Lateral view of female body, showing position of vulva; (B) lateral view of male head end, showing buccal cavity amphid and cervical setae; (C) lateral view of male tail, showing spicule and caudal glands; (D) lateral view of male anterior region, showing a cylindrical oesophagus; (E) lateral view of femal tail, showing three caudal glands." ;
